org.eclipse.scada.configuration.infrastructure

Interface Options

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OptionsImpl

    public interface Options
    A representation of the model object 'Options'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Base Da Ngp Port
    • Base Ae Ngp Port
    • Base Ca Ngp Port
    • Base Hd Ngp Port
    • Monitor Pools
    • Event Pools
    • Default User Service

    See Also:
    InfrastructurePackage.getOptions()
